OL,6,FA GP who performed CPR on a West
OL,7,FBromwich fan has described the
OL,8,Fcircumstances around his death as a
OL,9,F'shambles'.
OL,11,FMark Townsend, 57, fatally collapsed
OL,12,Fon 28 September 2024 at Hillsborough
OL,13,FStadium during a match between West
OL,14,FBromwich Albion and Sheffield
OL,15,FWednesday.
