OL,3,CResponse to West Brom supporter's
OL,4,Cdeath was a 'shambles', inquest told
OL,6,FDr Richard Stones, who was sat a few
OL,7,Fseats away from Mr Townsend, told an
OL,8,Finquest into his death that he started
OL,9,Fto do CPR on him when his sixth sense
OL,10,Fkicked in that he was in cardiac
OL,11,Farrest.
OL,13,FHe said the situation was "chaotic"
OL,14,Fand that there was no urgency or
OL,15,Fcommunication between people. He also
OL,16,Fsaid he overheard someone say a
OL,17,Fdefibrillator had run out of battery.
