OL,3,CResponse to West Brom supporter's
OL,4,Cdeath was a 'shambles', inquest told
OL,6,FMr Stones added that it was: "one of
OL,7,Fthe worst things I ever seen. No one
OL,8,Fwas listening. I wasn't listened to as
OL,9,Fa Doctor. No one was given anyone
OL,10,Finstructions".
OL,12,FThe GP told the inquest that a
OL,13,Fdecision was made to move Mr Townsend
OL,14,Fto the concourse behind the Leppings
OL,15,FLane stand, where he said there was
OL,16,F"more chaos".
