OL,6,FBut under questioning from the legal
OL,7,Fteam representing Sheffield Wednesday
OL,8,Fand Lambda Medical (an ambulance
OL,9,Fservice), it was put to Mr Stones that
OL,10,Fresponse was around 4 minutes and not
OL,11,Ften, and that he may not have been
OL,12,Fdoing CPR for as long as he stated as
OL,13,Fother people took over.
OL,15,F"There was a clear plan and leadership"
OL,17,FLewis Wright, the owner and director
OL,18,Fof Lambda Medical said: "There was a
OL,19,Fclear action plan throughout.
