OL,3,CResponse to West Brom supporter's
OL,4,Cdeath was a 'shambles', inquest told
OL,6,FJust days after Mr Townsend's death,
OL,7,Fhis brother, Steve Townsend, told ITV
OL,8,FNews Central that he wanted a
OL,9,FCoroner's Inquest to find out the full
OL,10,Fdetails of what happened and for a
OL,11,Freview across the country of how
OL,12,Ffootball stadiums respond to medical
OL,13,Femergencies like this.
OL,15,FFans were outraged the match was not
OL,16,Fstopped, criticising Sheffield
OL,17,FWednesday, and said there was no room
OL,18,Ffor mouth-to-mouth resuscitation.
