OL,3,CResponse to West Brom supporter's
OL,4,Cdeath was a 'shambles', inquest told
OL,6,FSheffield Wednesday released a
OL,7,Fstatement after the death, saying
OL,8,F"advanced paramedic care was at the
OL,9,Fscene applying emergency treatment
OL,10,Fwithin three minutes of the control
OL,11,Froom being notified, just over one
OL,12,Fminute after the nearest steward was
OL,13,Falerted".
OL,15,FThe inquest comes after a Sheffield
OL,16,FWednesday fan was sentenced in January
OL,17,Fthis year for mocking Mark's death on
OL,18,Fsocial media.
