OL,6,FAfter the match, Richard Crisp, 55,
OL,7,Freferenced the 1989 Hillsborough
OL,8,Fdisater, which killed 97 Liverpool
OL,9,Ffans, and wrote on X: "What are we at
OL,10,Fnow, 98? When we get to 100 we'll have
OL,11,Fa party."
OL,13,FHe was given a 12-month community
OL,14,Forder and ordered to pay #200 in costs.
OL,16,FHe later lost his project manager job,
OL,17,Fwas expelled from his golf club, and
OL,18,Fgiven a lifetime ban by Sheffield
OL,19,FWednesday.
OL,21,FThe inquest continues.
